r fem., meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Fourteenth,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "are subject to the same rules as"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "vaAliva Ea$ara", "text_ar": "ثَالِثَ عَشَرَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and its fem., expl. in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "vlv", "text_ar": "ثلث"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", q. v.] ―         -b5-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_ibilN rawaAbiEu", "text_ar": "اـِبِلٌ رَوَابِعُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Camels coming to water,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "being watered, on the fourth day, counting the day of the next preceding watering as the first"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": pl. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "raAbiEapN", "text_ar": "رَابِعَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: from"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rabaEati AlA_ibilu", "text_ar": "رَبَعَتِ الاـِبِلُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "waradati Alr~iboEa", "text_ar": "وَرَدَتِ الرِّبْعَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S, K.) In like manner, also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rawaAbEu", "text_ar": "رَوَابعُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is applied, metaphorically, to birds of the kind called"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qaTFA", "text_ar": "قَطًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", as an epithet denoting their coming to water, by El- 'Ajjáj. (TA.)       -A2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rabiyEN raAbiEN", "text_ar": "رَبِيعٌ رَابِعٌ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A fruitful,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "plentiful,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rbyE", "text_ar": "ربيع"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[meaning the season so called]. (ISk, K.) ―         -b2-  One does not say"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yawomN raAbiEN", "text_ar": "يَوْمٌ رَابِعٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "like as one says"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yawomN qaAy^iZN", "text_ar": "يَوْمٌ قَا